    • countWords

      List<String> countWords(List<String> inputList, Rule rule)
      参数:
      inputList - : String list before filter
      rule - : filter rule, including start string, end string, max length, min length, each condition can be null
      返回:
      String list after filter, if all conditions are null, return original string list
